Afisawa 4:30 tana gaya mana  cewa masu bada gaskiya an “hatimce ku da shi, cewa ku nasa ne a ranar fansa.” Idan masu bada gaskiya basu da tsarewar har abada ba, hatimcewa bata iya yiwuwa na gaske a ranar fansa ba, amma kaɗai ga ranar zunubi, fanɗarewa, ko rashin ibada.
Yahaya 3:15-16 na faɗi cewa duk wanda ke bada gaskiya cikin Yesu Kiristi zai “sami rai madawwami.” Idan da za a yi wa mutum alƙawarin rai madawwami, amma kuma a ɗauke ta, bata zama “madawwami” ba ce tun farko ma.
Gardama mafi ƙarfi don tsarewa ta har abada shine Romawa 8:38-39, “Domin na tabbata, ko mutuwa ce, ko rai, ko mala’iku, ko manyan mala’iku, ko al’amuran yanzu, ko al’amura masu zuwa, ko masu iko, ko tsawo, ko zurfi, kai ko kowace irin halitta ma, ba zasu iya raba mu da ƙaunar da Allah ke yi mana ta wurin Almasihu Yesu Ubangijinmu ba.” Tsarewarmu ta har abada ta zauna ne kan ƙaunar Allah ga waɗanda Shi ya fanshe su.
Littafi Mai Tsarki ta bayar da tafarki a zahiri zuwa rai madawwami.
“Gama ƴan adam duka sun yi zunubi, sun kasa kuma ga ɗaukakar Allah” (Romawa 3:23).
Tun da yake duk zunubanmu a ƙarshe gaba da Allah madawwami ne, sai dai hukunci madawwamiya ce ta isa.
“Gama sakamakon zunubi mutuwa ne, amma baiwar Allah ita ce rai madawwami cikin Almasihu Yesu Ubangijinmu” (Romawa 6:23).
